{"tid":1173342,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇得輸］樓價跌 最開心仍是業主","createTime":"2019-05-27T04:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:33:09.000Z","uid":13739,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0d2468b4fbdacd4bc5622661709b07290478db","tid":1173342,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"嘩！Google終止與華為合作，涉及Android的手機作業系統，好得人驚喎！不過任正非說得好：「美國的『90天臨時執照』（禁令寬限期）對我們沒有多大意義，我們已經做好了準備！」不談政治，不過在我這個消費者來說，我會放棄Google繼續用華為，我認為這個是消費者的尊嚴！消費者的選擇不應該被供應商擺佈！這個世界現在就是變成這樣，無論向好與否，其實大多數人心中都是由自己的喜惡去為事情作取捨！而不是根據客觀環境，例如，也如修訂《逃犯條例》，一些人不相信內地執法，向他說甚麼話也沒有用，他們都會認為是惡法，對信的人來說又會覺得有關條例沒有甚麼可怕。<br />\n<br />\n地產市場的好玩之處，是在於無論你的看法如何，市場很快就會印證到誰對誰錯！近期這麼多動盪消息難免會影響到市場氣氛，很多人又期望樓價下跌，我再說多次，樓價下跌可能對一些人來說，他們會感到開心！但其實最開心的一群仍然是業主！因為大部分業主其實都歡迎市場調節，因為愈調節他們的財富的泡沫就愈低，資產「含金量」就愈高！「樓價唔跌，哪有機會買多件！」所謂投資策略就是進和退都要留一線，要摸頂贏到盡或者要到谷底盡頭才肯入貨的，其實都會令到自己不能夠進退皆宜，買樓本是平常事，賺錢本著平常心！<br />\n<br />\n想樓價跌好易，支持政府造地啦！正經嘢唔做！才是令樓價拾級而上的主因！<br />\n<br />\n汪敦敬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190521/59626484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59626484&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=e9ebe875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59626484&h=09cf661b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190521/59626484</a><br />\n<br />\n廢淡點輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0295685e23d2d560b38164a0a8f119a4d20d83","tid":1173342,"uid":113373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=2cdb7724\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8903de421abcab0dadca52c98a5f323915703af0","tid":1173342,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d94574a6888f4e7a0ae3fcf9deaf78f0a320c90","tid":1173342,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"假既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70697f481a89e58f5aaa3215e894d04dd313fdff","tid":1173342,"uid":100256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8903de421abcab0dadca52c98a5f323915703af0","tid":1173342,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:02:33.000Z","msg":"好撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff182e7847170355f80e53c3b1ee2464370f3c12","tid":1173342,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8903de421abcab0dadca52c98a5f323915703af0","tid":1173342,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"低置仔偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3efe187bd8fbd8b38d615ba41a698cbbad9e2